Here are 5  facts you need to know One: The war started on October 7  when H@mas invaded  Israel, m@ssacred over  over 1,200 Israelis and kidnapped 240.  Number two: The IDF has two goals for  this war.  Number one:  return all the  hostages safely to their homes and number two:  Make sure that H@mas will no  longer face a  threat on Israelis.  Number three:  H@mas has been  caught numerous times stealing  the humanitarian  aid that was  facilitated by Israel and the  IDF. Humanitarian aid  that is meant  to go to the  people of Gaza. Number four:  H@mas has been  repeatedly operating  from civilian  infrastructure. Sensitive locations such as hospitals  schools, mosques  and kindergartners.  And fact number five:  IDF soldiers are  operating in  complete accordance  with our  code of conduct  and values of  the IDF according to international  law.
